# PDF Generation: LaTeX Only

**Never generate PDF from Markdown.** The research paper pipeline must always:

1. Produce LaTeX source (`paper.tex`) as the canonical format
2. Compile PDF using `pdflatex` + `bibtex` only
3. Never fall back to markdown-to-PDF (pandoc wkhtmltopdf, fpdf2, etc.)

If `pdflatex` is not available, report an error and instruct the user to install MiKTeX or TeX Live. Do not silently convert markdown to PDF.
